w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>File -> open -> select image -> click T and write text.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9e523f4b88ec553f0aece7048aa56b28/eea4a/Horizontaltype.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.86075949367089%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"text\"\n        title=\"text\"\n        src=\"/static/9e523f4b88ec553f0aece7048aa56b28/828fb/Horizontaltype.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9e523f4b88ec553f0aece7048aa56b28/ff44c/Horizontaltype.jpg 158w,\n/static/9e523f4b88ec553f0aece7048aa56b28/a6688/Horizontaltype.jpg 315w,\n/static/9e523f4b88ec553f0aece7048aa56b28/828fb/Horizontaltype.jpg 630w,\n/static/9e523f4b88ec553f0aece7048aa56b28/0ede0/Horizontaltype.jpg 945w,\n/static/9e523f4b88ec553f0aece7048aa56b28/3ac88/Horizontaltype.jpg 1260w,\n/static/9e523f4b88ec553f0aece7048aa56b28/eea4a/Horizontaltype.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>To create a line of text, Go to the <strong><em>Tools panel</em></strong> and select the <strong><em>Horizontal Type tool</em></strong>. Click your image where you would like to insert text and write anything. When you‚Äôre done, press Escape exiting the text field. Notice that a new layer with your text has appeared in the Layers panel.</p>\n<p>when you follow the above steps then it will create a text layer and will show on the text layer available on photoshop‚Äôs right side section.</p>\n<p>Thanks for reading‚Ä¶</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to add text to a photo in photoshop?","tags":["Photoshop"],"date":"March 14, 2022","description":"adding custom text in photoshop example with step by step guide with images - aGuidehub.","social_image":""}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to add background color in photoshop?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/how-to-add-background-color-in-photoshop/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to put a border around an image in photoshop?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/how-to-put-a-border-around-an-image-in-photoshop/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/how-to-add-text-to-a-photo-in-photoshop/","prevSlug":"/blog/how-to-add-background-color-in-photoshop/","nextSlug":"/blog/how-to-put-a-border-around-an-image-in-photoshop/"}},
